<chapter line="1">Saddabindu <pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0001" /> pakaraṇaṃ</chapter>
<centered line="2">Namo tassa bhagavato arahato sammāsambuddhassa</centered>
<hangnum line="3" number="1"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="4"> Yassañeyyesu dhammesu, nāṇumattampaveditaṃ,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="5">Natvāsaddhammasaṅghaṃtaṃ, saddabinduṃsamārabhe;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="6" number="2"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0002" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="7"> Kādiritā navasaṅkhyā, kamenaṭā di yādica,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="8">Pādayopañca saṅkhyātā, suññanāmā saraññanā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="9" number="3"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="10"> Sarehevasarāpubbe luttāvāvīpareramā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="11">Byañjanācāgamāvāvī dīgharassādisambhavā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="12" number="4"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0003" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="13"> Kākāsenāgatosisa keniddhimaccadassayi,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="14">Arājakhvaggimesīnaṃ sotukammeghayitthiyo;</gathalast>
<centered line="15">Iti sandhikappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="16" number="5"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0004" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="17"> Buddhapumayuvasanta rājabrahmasakhācasā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="18">Yatādidehījantuca satthupitābhibhūvidū;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="19" number="6"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="20"> Kaññāmmārattithipo, kkharaṇīnadirumātubhū,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="21">Napuṃsaketiyantāca, padakammadadhāyuno;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="22" number="7"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0005" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="23"> Gahitāgahaṇenettha suddhosyādyantakāpume,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="24">Vimalāhontijāntehi thyaṃpañcantehidādhikā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="25" number="8"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="26"> Napuṃsakepayogātu janakāhontityantato,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="27">Padhānānugatāsabba nāmasamāsataddhitā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="28" number="9"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0006" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="29"> Attiliṅgānipātādi tatoluttāvasyādayo,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="30">Suttānurūpatosiddhā hontivattāmanādayo;</gathalast>
<centered line="31">Iti nāmakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="32" number="10"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="33"> Chakārakesasāmismiṃ samāsohotisambhavā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="34">Taddhītākattukammasa, mpadānokāsasāmisu;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="35" number="11"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0007" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="36"> Sādhattayamhiākhyāto kitakosattasādhane,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="37">Sabbatthapaṭhamāvutte avuttedutiyādayo;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="38" number="12"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="39"> Manasāmuninovutyā vanebuddhenavaṇṇite,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="40">Vaṭṭāhitovivaṭṭatthaṃ bhikkhubhāvetibhāvanaṃ;</gathalast>
<centered line="41">Iti kārakakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="42" number="13"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0008" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="43"> Rāsīdvipadikādvandā liṅgenavacanenaca,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="44">Luttātulyādhikaraṇā bahubbīhītukhemarū;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="45" number="14"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="46"> Tappurisācakhemorā dayācakammadhārayā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="47">Digavocāvyayāhārā etesabbepihāritā;</gathalast>
<centered line="48">Iti samāsakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="49" number="15"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="50"> Kaccāditopiekamhā saddatoniyamaṃvinā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="51">Nekatthesatibhonteva sabbetaddhitapaccayā;</gathalast>
<centered line="52">Iti taddhitakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="53" number="16"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0009" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="54"> Kattarināññathākamme tathābhāvetumerayā,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="55">Sabbetepacadhātumhi saṅkhepenamarūmayā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="56" number="17"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0010" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="57"> Gamīmhātiguṇāphatto sambhavāaññadhātusu,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="58">Anantāvapayogāte ādesapaccayādihi;</gathalast>
<centered line="59">Iti ākhyātakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="60" number="18"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="61"> Kitādipaccayāsabbe, ekamhāapidhātuto,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="62">Siyuṃnurūpatosatta, sādhanesatipāyato;</gathalast>
<centered line="63">Iti kitakappo samatto.</centered>
<hangnum line="64" number="19"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0011" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="65"> Iminākiñcilesena, sakkāñātuṃjināgame,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="66">Payogāñāṇināsindhu, rasovekenabindunā;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="67" number="20"></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="68"> Rammaṃsīghappavesāya, puraṃpiṭakasaññitaṃ,</gatha1>
<gathalast line="69">Maggojumaggataṃmaggaṃ, saddāraññevisodhito;</gathalast>
<hangnum line="70" number="21"><pageBreak edition="V" number="0.0012" /></hangnum>
<gatha1 line="71"> Teneva kiñci jalito jalito padīpo</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="72">Kaccāyanuttiratano citagabbhakoṇe,</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="73">Dhammādirājagurunā garumāmakena</gatha3>
<gathalast line="74">Dhammena yobbipatinā sagaruttanīto;</gathalast>
<centered line="75">Iti saddabindu pakaraṇaṃ parisamattaṃ.</centered>
<gatha1 line="76">Yosaññamo guṇadhano nayanaṃ nijaṃva</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="77">Sikkhāpayī mama mavaṃ sugatāgamādo,</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="78">Salloka puñja suhado padumādi rāma</gatha3>
<gathalast line="79">Nāmo mahā yativarā cariyo samayhaṃ;</gathalast>
<gatha1 line="80">Saddhādhanena vasatā viditamhi pupphā</gatha1>
<gatha2 line="81">Rāmedhunā ariyavaṃsa dhajavhayena,</gatha2>
<gatha3 line="82">Santena ñāṇatilako tyaparākhyakena</gatha3>
<gathalast line="83">Bālānametamavidhīyi mayāhitāya;</gathalast>
